#### POST /api/users
Create a new user.

**Headers:**
```
Authorization: Bearer <token>
```

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "username": "newuser",
  "password": "password123",
  "department_id": 1,
  "role_ids": [1, 2],
  "sap_code": 12345,
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "p_num": "P123456",
  "full_name": "John Doe"
}
```

**Field Constraints:**
- `username`: Maximum 100 characters
- `password`: Will be hashed and stored (hash limit: 255 characters)
- `department_id`: Required - ID of the department the user belongs to (must reference an existing department)
- `role_ids`: Array of role IDs (at least one role is required)
- `sap_code`: Optional - SAP code (number)
- `email`: Optional - Email address (maximum 255 characters)
- `p_num`: Optional - Personnel number (maximum 100 characters)
- `full_name`: Optional - Full name (maximum 255 characters)

**Note:** 
- `role_ids` must be an array with at least one role ID
- Department assignments are managed separately via the `/api/users-departments` endpoint
- Regional assignments (sub divisions) are managed separately via the `/api/users-sub-divisions` endpoint

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "User created successfully",
  "data": {
    "id": 2,
    "username": "newuser",
    "sap_code": 12345,
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "p_num": "P123456",
    "full_name": "John Doe",
    "is_active": true,
    "created_at": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
    "updated_at": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

**Error Responses:**
- `400` - Username, password, and role_ids (array with at least one role) are required
- `400` - department_id is required
- `400` - department_id must be a valid positive number
- `400` - Department not found
- `400` - Username already exists

