**Note:** The following fields have restrictions:
- `status` - Cannot be updated through this endpoint. Use the action endpoints instead:
  - `PUT /api/bpd-materials/:id/actions/allocate` - to allocate a material (status 0 → 1)
  - `PUT /api/bpd-materials/:id/actions/use` - to use a material (status 1 → 2)
- `r_qty` - Can be updated through this endpoint, but only when material status is 0 (required). It can also be set when creating the material.
- `alloc_qty` - Can be updated through this endpoint, but only when material status is 1 (allocated). It can also be set when allocating via the allocate action endpoint.
- `act_qty` - Can be updated through this endpoint, but only when material status is 2 (installed). It can also be set when using via the use action endpoint.
- `req_remarks` - Can be updated through this endpoint, but only when material status is 0 (required). It can also be set when creating the material.
- `alloc_remarks` - Can be updated through this endpoint, but only when material status is 1 (allocated). It can also be set when allocating via the allocate action endpoint.
- `act_remarks` - Can be updated through this endpoint, but only when material status is 2 (installed). It can also be set when using via the use action endpoint.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "BPD material updated successfully",
  "data": {
    "bpdm_id": 1,
    "bpd_id": 1,
    "m_id": 2,
    "r_qty": 120.00,
    "req_remarks": "Updated requirement"
  }
}
```

**Error Responses:**
- `400` - Invalid BPD material ID
- `400` - Status cannot be updated through this endpoint. Use the action endpoints instead.
- `400` - r_qty can only be updated when material status is 0 (required). Current status is X.
- `400` - alloc_qty can only be updated when material status is 1 (allocated). Current status is X.
- `400` - act_qty can only be updated when material status is 2 (installed). Current status is X.
- `400` - req_remarks can only be updated when material status is 0 (required). Current status is X.
- `400` - alloc_remarks can only be updated when material status is 1 (allocated). Current status is X.
- `400` - act_remarks can only be updated when material status is 2 (installed). Current status is X.
- `400` - Invalid BPD ID or Material ID
- `404` - BPD material not found

