### Project Issues

**Access Restrictions:**
- **Department Restriction**: Users can only see project issues that belong to business plans in their assigned department (based on `users.department_id`)
- **Regional Restriction**: Users can only see project issues that belong to business plans in their allowed sub divisions (via `users_sd` table)
- Both restrictions are applied together - users must have access to both the department and sub-division to see a project issue

